79068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cce583ffc507c693f2c4f4c5cd8b835a87e199a","tid":1393661,"uid":279068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"成日聽到大家鬧人唔識入迴旋處，咁8月5日大家唔返工晨早6醒咗，集會又冇咁早，咁不如一齊出嚟示範下指教下啦。以下係精選位置同埋少少介紹：<br />\n<br />\n大圍車公廟路迴旋處 &ndash; 五星級難度，祝君好運<br />\n觀塘港鐵站迴旋處 &ndash; 成個觀塘靠曬佢<br />\n元朗博愛交匯處 &ndash; 唔洗講啦，今次點少得佢<br />\n十八鄉交匯處 &ndash; 同樓上係friend<br />\n大埔廣福邨迴旋處 &ndash; 成個大埔出九龍靠曬佢<br />\n上水雞嶺迴旋處 &ndash; 雞嶺一塞&hellip;&hellip;諗起都想打冷震<br />\n荃錦交匯處 &ndash; 呢個平時都轉到自己唔知應該邊度出<br />\n石門迴旋處 &ndash; 唔係好熟, 不過有人話好玩<br />\n青衣担杆山交匯處 - 唔係好熟, 不過有人話好玩<br />\n青衣南迴旋處 &ndash; 青衣命脈<br />\n九龍城迴旋處 &ndash; 亂到唔識形容<br />\n<br />\n為咗慳油留力，大家去返自己區都可以，有乜嘢就be water啦，有好風景記住望多兩眼。師傅教落冇車同有信心先好出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AvGZp7y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvGZp7y.jpg&h=42f578e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YpVGDsy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYpVGDsy.jpg&h=a742dd70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7hj8isy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7hj8isy.jpg&h=c85a27be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kj4DFFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkj4DFFU.jpg&h=f0a32bba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DPMq47z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPMq47z.jpg&h=8399c26f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXEzYsz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXEzYsz.jpg&h=ead56070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdSqkFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdSqkFU.jpg&h=9c9bca32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/amPzYsz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FamPzYsz.jpg&h=9cfaef16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9bNqkFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9bNqkFV.jpg&h=cfa9f6af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJVvwNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJVvwNA.jpg&h=cb685f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dr8pBef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdr8pBef.jpg&h=6c5fd566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FofZ9zf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFofZ9zf.jpg&h=7fd70239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n時刻保持安全車速，小心駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港　時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"加多個荃青交匯處<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TDEL5BY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTDEL5BY.jpg&h=5668cabb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7723de09c13783709fba2a03e9bf24be14680de2","tid":1393661,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d884673c199a557d994a4d8a2c25d591228fbe","tid":1393661,"uid":197110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"681c5cf6cf3ed64e9228460d3a9073ac8c844a5d","tid":1393661,"uid":104308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:18:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"67d06726e4473925e5589df77f59e07d5cddfc17","tid":1393661,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class